Description
===========
JS, CSS linter and PHP fixer just in a single command.
It is built under Grunt.

Installation standalone
============
*For intergrating to a project*

1. Download zip file
2. Unzip file to the root-path-of-project
3. Configure the paths according to the project
4. Commit/push as a part of the project.

Run linter
==========
1. Install packages
```
npm install
```

2. Run the command
``` 
grunt linter 
```